name: Leaf Blade
summary: Dead damage, and has an increased critical hit ratio.
viability: Leaf Blade is an extremely good move for physical Grass types like Victreebel and SD Sceptile. It also works as a good coverage move for Gallade. For Farfetch'd, it's excellent because of the increased critical hit ratio. In conjunction with its Stick item, the chances of a crit are near perfect.
